enhanced_by.reason: The birthday method is invoked to determine the birth date, which is crucial for generating the ID number.
The gender method is invoked to determine the gender, which influences the 7th digit of the ID number.
The get7thDigit method calculates the 7th digit of the ID number, which is directly related to the output of generateValid.
The generateDay method formats the birth date into the first 6 digits of the ID number, which is part of the output of generateValid.
